  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Fabric to finished garment transformation at cut-and-sew facility.",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries GS1 product master data plus product-level",
    "textile classification (textileCategory / apparelSubcategory / fabricType) on the",
    "output garment; those describe the GTIN, not a specific lot. No ilmd is used",
    "because we have no lot-specific data to carry on this event.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,textile=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/textile/",
    "See: core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
